

Title: Community Challenge: What are you building with LeafEngines?

Category: Show and Tell

Body:

Community Challenge: Share Your LeafEngines Projects!

To our amazing community of 1,106 cloners** (and counting!), we want to know:

What are YOU building with LeafEngines?

Reward: 30 Days LeafEngines Pro FREE

How to Participate:
1. Comment below with your use case
2. OR create a new issue labeled "use-case"
3. OR tweet about it and tag @LeafEnginesAI

What We're Looking For:
- Agricultural automation projects
- MCP server integrations
- Claude skill enhancements  
- Research applications
- Commercial implementations
- Even conceptual ideas!

Why This Matters:
We've discovered our community is:
- Highly technical (576% clone-to-view ratio!)
- Globally distributed** (>50% outside major markets)
- Cross-domain (MCP + AgriTech + Claude ecosystem)

Understanding your use cases helps us build better tools for YOU.

Timeline:
- Submit by April 18, 2026
- Pro access delivered within 48 hours
- Featured use cases will be highlighted in our docs!

